    scSub: {es: 'Un agente correla logs multi-servicio, arma la línea temporal y propone un post-mortem blameless. La publicación exige firma del incident commander.', en: 'An agent correlates multi-service logs, builds the timeline and drafts a blameless post-mortem. Publication requires incident-commander sign-off.'},
